{"tid":291411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙鬥牛勇士遭牛角穿肺亡  離場遺言：我快死了","createTime":"2017-06-20T14:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T15:06:00.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"050c6888b0bbcc09ad6e68ada25caaff92f6ca8c","tid":291411,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"西班牙36歲鬥牛士費甸盧（Ivan Fandino）日前在鬥牛表演中，被發狂的公牛用角刺胸，他的肺部重創而死，這位已為人父的鬥牛士遺言曝光，透露出他受傷後的恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n已為人父的費甸盧在法國一場鬥牛表演中失手受傷，其他鬥牛士合力將他抬離場，他當時非常驚恐地催促：「快手，我快死了！」但他送院途中不治，這一句說話成為他的遺言。<br />\n<br />\n費甸盧曾經獲獎，有12年經驗，但他早前表演鬥牛時雙腳似乎被其斗篷絆倒，被公牛撞飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，當他跌在地上時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，公牛用角刺向他胸部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，把他的肺刺穿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。觀眾當時渾然不知費甸盧重傷，「民眾一開始仍然為他歡呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，以為情況受控」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170620/20062335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170620%2F20062335&d=0s4k466Ec1exW3L0JB69msmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=265025e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170620%2F20062335&h=3421599f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170620/20062335</a></div><br />\n<br />\n這是一年內第二宗鬥牛士命喪鬥牛場的慘劇，再度引發社會激辯鬥牛活動何去何從。鬥牛有深厚歷史及文化意義，西班牙皇室、首相拉霍伊（Mariano Rajoy）等人都發聲明悼念費甸盧，但愛護動物組織批評鬥牛活動殘忍，為了娛樂逼使牛隻痛苦中死亡，「每場鬥牛都是悲劇，牠們無法避免要經歷漫長而痛苦的死亡過程」，認為鬥牛早應該成為歷史。"},{"pid":"ddeaec78033ae641b1af57174a53e9f93e3ceb70","tid":291411,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:30:12.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"6abfbea60059969ab99f5026d46e2106e5f42a0d","tid":291411,"uid":37005,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:31:09.000Z","msg":"抵死 全部有份參與鬥牛嘅人都仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82e58e6c916a66912c48d61a9c1b8758a3079c4","tid":291411,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:31:34.000Z","msg":"國際人道協會表示，鬥牛士之死是一場悲劇，但每年在鬥牛中慘遭殺害的公牛有1000頭，沒有人或動物應該為了娛樂而失去生命。<br />\n<br />\n鬥牛在西班牙已有數百年歷史，仍受民眾歡迎。加泰羅尼亞在2012年禁止這項活動，但在去年10月遭憲法法院推翻。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://imgs.ntdtv.com/pic/2017/6-18/p8250024a896059481.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.ntdtv.com%2Fpic%2F2017%2F6-18%2Fp8250024a896059481.jpg&h=9de0b559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2017年6月17日，西班牙鬥牛士范丁諾在法國西南部鬥牛時，意外被斗篷絆倒在地。(IROZ GAIZKA/AFP/Getty Images)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.ntdtv.com/pic/2017/6-18/p8250022a478998230.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.ntdtv.com%2Fpic%2F2017%2F6-18%2Fp8250022a478998230.jpg&h=12a6e14c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">被牛刺傷。(IROZ GAIZKA/AFP/Getty Images)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.ntdtv.com/pic/2017/6-18/p8250025a415786635.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.ntdtv.com%2Fpic%2F2017%2F6-18%2Fp8250025a415786635.jpg&h=14b68a46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">他被同伴抬離時，臉部露出痛苦的表情。(IROZ GAIZKA/AFP/Getty Images)</span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2017/06/18/a1329667.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fxtr%2Fb5%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2Fa1329667.html&d=0s4k466Ec1exW3L0JB69msmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=720fded7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2017/06/18/a1329667.html</a></div>"},{"pid":"7173ed077820330e4ab079c615a932c4aa5fe489","tid":291411,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:37:47.000Z","msg":"🤷🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"816fc6db04ee7bc875a8e249d55a74c044be594e","tid":291411,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:41:40.000Z","msg":"你有武器隻牛冇<br />\n隻牛仲以為打敗你有活路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2169bb190f6d28e0f90243e4bad8f2036266f5e","tid":291411,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:42:43.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"39a9e2211bf4aa4b659504fa29d0bca8b4059485","tid":291411,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:49:53.000Z","msg":"一早話西班牙低賤"},{"pid":"c26d6a3b916205e345ecef0b76fb2a317d711f2b","tid":291411,"uid":118771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:54:28.000Z","msg":"一句歷史傳統要保留<br />\n一年就有咁多隻牛俾人咁樣玩死"},{"pid":"bb34b40e99caf82a29ef21d591d43caee9ceb2ee","tid":291411,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:56:49.000Z","msg":"斗蓬殺左好多人"},{"pid":"47f4e37bcfbb6aa943f0ebd556df8d071c54a800","tid":291411,"uid":5684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef833504faee2847af4394945f1b639c038d1dee","tid":291411,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:02:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b36cfde78107024ac0353e77155f8229b32bbd9","tid":291411,"uid":119591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:04:00.000Z","msg":"求片"},{"pid":"a24224dd57f08d7ea2c7ad8f473dde9caf44f843","tid":291411,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:05:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bae197b5be70a99faed1fe592238379cd023afec","tid":291411,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:06:00.000Z","msg":"牛： 你班仆街，攞我奶食我肉煎我啲皮做手袋銀包又攞我黎玩，咩7都係我"}]}